  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SwordTrip: A Chinese-style Action Roguelite VR Game  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock powerful abilities through stage rewards, and utilize a skill system specifically designed for VR interaction to build your preferred skill combinations. Experience overwhelming power to defeat your enemies!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**<strong>A More Exciting Combat System</strong>**: Enjoy the thrill of sword clashes and slashes without the frustration of weapons getting stuck.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/3ba01dda727231f9404443f6b2453bf2.poster.avif?t=1739934508\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/3ba01dda727231f9404443f6b2453bf2.webm?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/3ba01dda727231f9404443f6b2453bf2.mp4?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**<strong>Skill System</strong>**: A VR-interaction-based skill system designed to amaze you with every ability!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/df7e68533c9e4d81dda2e8c617bc9935.poster.avif?t=1739934508\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/df7e68533c9e4d81dda2e8c617bc9935.webm?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/df7e68533c9e4d81dda2e8c617bc9935.mp4?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**<strong>Culturally Immersive Lobby</strong>**: Interact with Chinese culture in the game lobby, where you can write or paint with a calligraphy brush and customize the images on the lobby's display board.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/a91bed0cc6cb3ac0c65191d00bcab95b.poster.avif?t=1739934508\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/a91bed0cc6cb3ac0c65191d00bcab95b.webm?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/a91bed0cc6cb3ac0c65191d00bcab95b.mp4?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SwordTrip: A Chinese-style Action Roguelite VR Game  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock powerful abilities through stage rewards, and utilize a skill system specifically designed for VR interaction to build your preferred skill combinations. Experience overwhelming power to defeat your enemies!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**<strong>A More Exciting Combat System</strong>**: Enjoy the thrill of sword clashes and slashes without the frustration of weapons getting stuck.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/3ba01dda727231f9404443f6b2453bf2.poster.avif?t=1739934508\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/3ba01dda727231f9404443f6b2453bf2.webm?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/3ba01dda727231f9404443f6b2453bf2.mp4?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**<strong>Skill System</strong>**: A VR-interaction-based skill system designed to amaze you with every ability!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/df7e68533c9e4d81dda2e8c617bc9935.poster.avif?t=1739934508\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/df7e68533c9e4d81dda2e8c617bc9935.webm?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/df7e68533c9e4d81dda2e8c617bc9935.mp4?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**<strong>Culturally Immersive Lobby</strong>**: Interact with Chinese culture in the game lobby, where you can write or paint with a calligraphy brush and customize the images on the lobby's display board.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/a91bed0cc6cb3ac0c65191d00bcab95b.poster.avif?t=1739934508\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/a91bed0cc6cb3ac0c65191d00bcab95b.webm?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2899670/extras/a91bed0cc6cb3ac0c65191d00bcab95b.mp4?t=1739934508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
